webpack: module bundle

1. every file is module
2. use loaders to resolve module
3. use plugins to optimize chunk
4. code split , using when spa
5. support CMD/AMD/COMMONjs


1. browser js模块化
    1. CMD  define/module.exports/exports
    2. AMD  define/module.exports/exports/return

2. server node Commonjs
    require/module.exports

--webpack support all of that and I suggest Commonjs or es6(use babel loader)


entry: single or muli (string || array || object)

loaders: tpl/coffeescript/jade/png/css

plugins: commonPlugins

code split: require.ensure,
            merge chunk(MIN/MAX)

surroudings:
dev: cache/devtool/
prod: dedupe/compress/optimize

cli/node api
webpack (read webpack.config.js
webpack({
//configuration
}, callback)
